parameters:
Zerachiel: I'm not really in the mood
right now.

Zerachiel: Since my weapons have been
confiscated, I'll need to procure some
from the weapon shop first...

Zerachiel: I can't defeat monsters
barehanded, you know.

Zerachiel: Also, it seems like it would
be better to hide the angel wings and
halo before going outside.
Azel: Thank you all for gathering here.

Azel: Today, I have received some
intriguing information, so I have come
to share it with you all.

Azel: Do you know about the Great Tree
of the Magic Continent?

Mel: Are you talking about the Holy Tree
where the Seventh Curse was once
activated?

Aries: It seems to be growing near the
Vale, doesn't it?

Azel: We call it the Dreaming Great
Tree...

Azel: And there, the Six-Winged Angel
has been discovered.

Azel: Yes, it seems my subordinate
witnessed it.

Azel: They say she had long hair that
gave off a twilight-like impression,
with a fleeting atmosphere...

Lala: Master Ern, there's no mistake
about it!!

Azel: I also had a feeling like that, so
I wanted to let you know first.

Azel: We need to take action because of
the matter with the Star God, you know.

Claudia: So basically, you need to
confirm her identity before the knight
order does.

Claudia: Once the knight order starts
moving, we won't be able to get close
either.

Rabi: I see. If it's for Lala's sake,
I'll help out!

Zerachiel: Well then, let's prepare and
head out.

Zerachiel: You will move us to the Demon
Continent, right? Marnagarm.
Marnagarm: Ah, let me lend you a hand.

Azel: Well then, everyone, please take
care of me.

※Sachia has become a member of our
group.
※Rabi has become a member of our group.

Claudia has become a member of our
group.
※Lala has become a member of our group.

※Pururin has become a member of our
group.

The following is a scenario intended for those who have
played the previous game "Artemis of Paradise".

If you started with this game, there may be parts of the
story that are unclear. Please understand.
